default’ rights approach. 
defaultKalayaan
default has historically had a lot of trust from domestic workers, from community members. Domestic workers hear of us and come to us because they have been told that they can trust us and we will give them impartial advice. I have no doubt that, if word got out that people would be referred, even anonymously, into the NRM, there would be confusion around that, and numbers coming to us would drop and people would stop trusting us.
