defaultKalayaan
default will deliver a safe and confidential service. Terms such as “victim” and “trafficking” are unfamiliar to most domestic workers when they come to us, but I would be worried that people would start to think that we were part of the Government, and if they came to us they would be referred automatically to the Government and this would be unsafe for them.
